item.dc:creator: @dudeofthed dudeofthed
item.description:
@dudeofthed wrote:

Enough begging and let’s get started. Sorry we couldn’t help but i thought that you figured it out already since it was an old thread.

Here are a few questions i have to ask before continuing:

  1. Did you set the dimensions?
  2. Did you let it automatically log in?
  3. Which bank slot are you in?
  4. What Runescape brightness level is needed to use SL PSWW?
  5. What Runescape brightness level are you currently using?
  6. Did you read and full understand the instructions?

Just answer like this:

  1. Yes/No
  2. Yes/No
  3. Yes/No
  4. Yes/No
  5. Yes/No
  6. Yes/No

Answer any of those and reply to this message. Do not quote please.
